name: Wars Not Make One Great (V)
Lore: 'A Jedi seeks nonviolent solutions to problems, but may fight to preserve the existence of life. An apprentice must learn which battles to fight and which to avoid.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. During battles where your Jedi is present, players may not draw more than two battle destiny. Once during your turn, may take Inner Strength into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
